BuiltinFormatString Class Reference

#include <TimeTextCtrl.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

struct to hold a formatting control string and it's user facing name Used in an array to hold the built-in time formats that are always available to the user

BuiltinFormatString is a structure used in the TimeTextCtrl and holds both a descriptive name for the string format and a printf inspired style format string, optimised for displaying time in different formats.
